The paper also mentions the use of temporal propositional logic, which falls under the category of logic in computer science (cs.LO). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of argumentation theory, which is a subfield of philosophy and computer science (cs.PL). The paper also mentions the formalisation of problem domains, which is a common topic in multi-agent systems (cs.MA). Finally, the paper discusses the frame, qualification, and ramification problems, which are all related to the study of causality and change in computer science (cs.CC).
